{"parse":{"title":"Raw Greater Sagefish","pageid":44481,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|s=1|c=25}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_21\n|quality=Common\n|charges=1\n|ilvl=40\n|name=Raw Greater Sagefish\n|level=30\n|effect=Use: Restores 567 health and 882 mana over 21 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Source ==\nGreater Sagefish pools can be found in a variety of places throughout Azeroth:\n* Frequently in lakes, ponds, and rivers: [[Northern Stranglethorn]], [[Western Plaguelands]], [[Eastern Plaguelands]], [[Feralas]], [[Stonetalon Mountains]], [[Arathi Highlands]], and [[Blasted Lands]].\n* Occasionally: [[Moonglade]], The [[Hinterlands]], [[Stranglethorn Vale]], [[Desolace]], [[Hillsbrad Foothills]], [[Un'Goro Crater]], and The [[Cape of Stranglethorn]]\n* Rarely: [[Dustwallow Marsh]] and [[Thousand Needles]].\n\nAlso [[Outland]]: a few in the center of [[Serpentshrine Cavern]].\n\n== Raw Greater Sagefish as an ingredient ==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Sagefish Delight}}\n\n== External links ==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|21153}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_greater_sagefish.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]"}}}